{"id":475,"ayahs":[{"number":67,"arabic":"هُوَ ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَكُم مِّن تُرَابٍۢ ثُمَّ مِن نُّطْفَةٍۢ ثُمَّ مِنْ عَلَقَةٍۢ ثُمَّ يُخْرِجُكُمْ طِفْلًۭا ثُمَّ لِتَبْلُغُوٓا۟ أَشُدَّكُمْ ثُمَّ لِتَكُونُوا۟ شُيُوخًۭا ۚ وَمِنكُم مَّن يُتَوَفَّىٰ مِن قَبْلُ ۖ وَلِتَبْلُغُوٓا۟ أَجَلًۭا مُّسَمًّۭى وَلَعَلَّكُمْ تَعْقِلُونَ","translation":"It is He who creates you out of dust, and then out of a drop of sperm, and then out of a germ-cell; and then He brings you forth as children; and then [He ordains] that you reach maturity, and then, that you grow old - though some of you [He causes to] die earlier -: and [all this He ordains] so that you might reach a term set [by Him], and that you might [learn to] use your reason.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4200.mp3","surahId":40,"words":[{"id":58133,"position":1,"arabic":"هُوَ","translation":"তিনিই (আল্লাহ)","audioUrl":"wbw/040_067_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":58134,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/040_067_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":58135,"position":3,"arabic":"خَلَقَكُم","translation":"তোমাদের সৃষ্টি করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/040_067_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":58136,"position":4,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/040_067_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":58137,"position":5,"arabic":"تُرَابٍۢ","translation":"মাটি","audioUrl":"wbw/040_067_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":58138,"position":6,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/040_067_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":58139,"position":7,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/040_067_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":58140,"position":8,"arabic":"نُّطْفَةٍۢ","translation":"শুক্রবিন্দু","audioUrl":"wbw/040_067_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":58141,"position":9,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/040_067_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":58142,"position":10,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"থেকে","audioUr